precis:
Amendment to the PART VII EXEMPTION REGULATIONS exempting from notification
to the Agency of internal reorganizations implemented by corporations
involving either directly or indirectly the acquisition of a transportation
undertaking where both the acquiror and the transportation undertaking are
owned by one person.
